<HEADLINE> John Danforth Biographical Info </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NAME -- John Claggett Danforth  
</P>
<P>
	AGE-BIRTH DATE -- 63, Sept. 5, 1936  
</P>
<P>
	HOMETOWN -- St. Louis  
</P>
<P>
	EDUCATION -- Graduated Princeton University in 1963, received  
degrees from Yale Divinity School and Yale Law School 
</P>
<P>
	POLITICAL PARTY -- Republican  
</P>
<P>
