<HEADLINE> Olano Takes Lead at Tour of Spain </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	CIUDAD RODRIGO, Spain (AP) -- Jan Ullrich ended fellow German  
cyclist Marcel Wust's three-day winning streak by taking the fifth 
stage of the Tour of Spain on Thursday, and defending champion 
Abraham Olano replaced Wust as the overall leader. 
</P>
