it crashed at the mouth of Kern River Canyon. 
</P>
<P>
	The fire began as a handful of small arson blazes Wednesday and  
spread across grasslands and campgrounds between Bakersfield and 
Lake Isabella. 
</P>
<P>
	Firefighters had the fire contained by Thursday evening. One  
firefighter was treated for dehydration. 
  	   	
