been leading the company since 1996, will leave Jan. 1. At its peak 
in 1989, Esprit had 80 stores and discount outlets around the 
country. Now it has only 20 stores nationwide. Esprit has recently 
began targeting a slightly older customer by offering higher 
quality and slightly more expensive clothes. 

